 12 年来首次观看 Pulp 演奏“Bar Italia” https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pulp-play-bar-italia-for-first-time-in-12-years-3768123?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=watch-pulp-play-意大利酒吧 12 年来首次Damian JonesMon, 24 Jun 2024 11:20:09 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3768123 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_pulp_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="纸浆公司贾维斯·科克" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_pulp_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_pulp_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_pulp_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_pulp_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_pulp_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_pulp_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首歌是他们 1995 年经典专辑“Different Class”的收尾曲</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pulp-play-bar-italia-for-first-time-in-12-years-3768123">Watch Pulp 的后剧“Bar Italia”12 年来首次</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_pulp_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="纸浆公司贾维斯·科克" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_pulp_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_pulp_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_pulp_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_pulp_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_pulp_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2024_pulp_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>昨晚（6 月 23 日）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pulp">Pulp</a>在意大利 12 年来首次表演“Bar Italia”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jarvis-cocker-teases-more-pulp-shows-and-discusses-new-project-biophobia-i-used-to-be-scared-of-nature-3595600">贾维斯·科克 (Jarvis Cocker) 取笑更多低俗节目并讨论新项目“生物恐惧症”：“我曾经害怕大自然”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌曲以位于伦敦 Soho 区弗里斯街的一家意大利咖啡馆为背景，是他们 1995 年经典专辑《Different Class》的收尾曲。</p><p>这首歌将这家咖啡馆描述为“在苏荷区的拐角处”和“所有破碎的人都去的地方”，并且可以看到乐队坐在他们经典热门歌曲“Common People”的艺术品上。</p><p>许多歌迷表示很高兴听到乐队自 2012 年以来在 Medimex 音乐节上首次演奏这首歌曲，其中一位歌迷<a href="https://x.com/streetlites_/status/1805053729244156406">在 X 上写道</a>：“Pulp 今晚以 Bar Italia 结束了他们的演出，这是《Different Class》的最后一首歌曲，是史诗般的。”</p><p>另一位补充道：“意大利酒吧玩纸浆？？？到底是什么鬼？？？？”</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">我简直不敢相信<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f62d.png" alt="??" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/wKFcGep6AD">pic.twitter.com/wKFcGep6AD</a></p><p> - 酯 (@kIopptimistic) <a href="https://twitter.com/kIopptimistic/status/1805014300198641997?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 6 月 23 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>乐队还表演了一系列职业生涯亮点，包括《This Is Hardcore》、《Do You Remember The First Time?》、《Common People》、《Something Changed》和《Underwear》。</p><p>早些时候，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jarvis-cocker">贾维斯·科克 (Jarvis Cocker)</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-jesus-and-mary-chain">The Jesus &amp; Mary Chain</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pulps-jarvis-cocker-join-the-jesus-mary-chain-for-just-like-honey-3767980">在音乐节演出期间合作表演了《Just Like Honey》</a> 。</p><p>这些独立偶像已经<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pulp-announce-first-full-show-of-2024-amsterdam-buy-tickets-3599673">安排了许多夏季欧洲音乐节</a>，包括 Way Out West、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oya-festival-2024-adds-queens-of-the-stone-age-the-smile-the-national-and-more-3553501">Øya</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/flow-festival-announces-pulp-pj-harvey-the-smile-fred-again-and-more-for-stacked-2024-line-up-3547974">Flow Festival</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jarvis-cocker-teases-more-pulp-shows-and-discusses-new-project-biophobia-i-used-to-be-scared-of-nature-3595600">在今年 3 月接受<em>NME</em>采访时</a>，主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jarvis-cocker">贾维斯·科克 (Jarvis Cocker)</a>证实，该乐队的巡演计划将延长至 2025 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pulp-add-more-shows-to-first-north-america-tour-in-over-a-decade-3605361">。此后，他们宣布将于今年秋季举行十多年来的首次北美巡演</a>。</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pulp-debut-new-song-background-noise-live-in-mexico-3542753">Pulp 于 12 月在墨西哥的一场演出中首次推出了新歌“Background Noise</a> ”。鼓手 Nick Banks <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pulps-nick-banks-on-his-new-memoir-the-bands-future-and-the-joke-of-britpop-3509203">最近也向 NME 暗示，乐队可能会推出更多新材料</a>，但对很快就会有新音乐并不确定。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pulp-play-bar-italia-for-first-time-in-12-years-3768123">Watch Pulp 的后剧“Bar Italia”12 年来首次</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
